{"tid":2105544,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"肥就唔值得被尊重？","createTime":"2020-07-12T16:59:44.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-14T20:35:09.000Z","uid":208642,"like":31,"dislike":140,"uniUserReply":74,"replies":[{"pid":"f8f4a86cbef0bc53d5eb7cce6b20c45fbd61546e","tid":2105544,"uid":208642,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-07-12T16:59:44.000Z","msg":"好撚心你啲男人 唔鍾意肥婆咪出聲<br />\n同你講咗 打定底 又話唔介意先應承出街<br />\n出到嚟嫌樣衰飯都唔食走咗...<br />\n都係想要小小尊重姐<br />\n<br />\n姐係好撚傷自尊 係咪唔識諗人感受？<br />\n明明有節食 食中藥 做運動 都減唔到<br />\n肥真係唔係自己想<br />\n<br />\n肥婆都想被愛....而唔係每次用交友app 開始放個心落去 都只係被人呃蝦條<br />\n<br />\n講完，戥朋友唔抵only"},{"pid":"444201d85c76bef70d03a23242c79642178bc718","tid":2105544,"uid":361025,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-12T17:00:31.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"d3e3b6bd6138451d6b606a9d21c72f1b3db400ca","tid":2105544,"uid":2419,"like":15,"dislike":3,"score":12,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-12T17:00:54.000Z","msg":"<span class=\"xx-large\"><span class=\"red\"><strong>係</strong></span></span>"},{"pid":"2ac8dbc044f4dfd82f07a626cf818b1e2bd7a369","tid":2105544,"uid":72228,"like":71,"dislike":8,"score":63,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-12T17:02:05.000Z","msg":"肥 係可以改變<br />\n你話你天生有缺陷<br />\n點搞都搞唔翻嘅 <br />\n咁d人唔尊敬你<br />\n都情有可原<br />\n宜家你肥啵<br />\n你expect人點包容你<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a5db86f2d734710e98cfec2e734ba3a09df6a929","tid":2105544,"uid":143305,"like":16,"dislike":1,"score":15,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-12T17:02:45.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://evchk.wikia.org/zh/wiki/%E8%82%A5%E6%98%AF%E5%8E%9F%E7%BD%AA\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fevchk.wikia.org%2Fzh%2Fwiki%2F%25E8%2582%25A5%25E6%2598%25AF%25E5%258E%259F%25E7%25BD%25AA&d=Z5C23SoLFrdwUrTWaDZos4E4T4y%2BYV5jPOnVoTo%2FPYs%3D&h=7ac2acdd\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://evchk.wikia.org/zh/wiki/%E8%82%A5%E6%98%AF%E5%8E%9F%E7%BD%AA</a><br />\n<br />\n廢事貼出嚟"},{"pid":"30364fdc760edad255a706602d5e80d4c9a2